summary: My personal bodyslide preset well my new one along with my racemenu preset made from scratch. Enjoy them! The Duo team uses this body too.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Tahoma][size=4]This is my latest bodyslide preset. It's based off of 7 base original and 7 base unp since those are two of my favorite bodies. I hope you guys all enjoy! I also included my racemenu preset for those that wish to use it. 

[/size][/font][size=4]Bodyslide Requirements:
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015]Bodyslide and Outfit Studio[/url]﻿

Preset Requirements:
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602]Fair Skin Complexion[/url]﻿
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7625/]numenume femalebrows MARO. may need to put your textures to high to avoid pixelated brows.[/url]﻿
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos Renewal[/url]﻿
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82588]Improved Eyes Skyrim[/url]﻿
[font=Lucida Sans Unicode]
[/font][font=Lucida Sans Unicode]Credits:
Thanks to Caliente and Ousnius for Bodyslide; [/font][/size][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][size=4]Crosscrusade, DeMoNhUnTeR1986, and Sevennity for SevenBase; dimon99 for dimonized unp body.
[/size][/font]
